<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>OTP Verification</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: auto;
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            color: #4CAF50;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .otp {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #4CAF50;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .details {
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding: 15px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border-left: 4px solid #4CAF50;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .details p {
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 14px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #777;
        }
        .footer p {
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>OTP Verification for <%= name %></h1>
        <p>Your OTP is:</p>
        <div class="otp"><%= otp %></div>
        <div class="details">
            <p>Master Name: <strong><%= masterName %></strong></p>
            <p>Category Name: <strong><%= catName %></strong></p>
        </div>
        <p>Please enter this OTP in the application to verify your account.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>If you did not request this, please ignore this email.</p>
        <p>Thank you for using our service!</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>